</colgroup>
<thead class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p>Type</p></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p>Status</p></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p>Date&nbsp;</p></t=
h>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p>Description</p></=
th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p>Impact</p></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p>Mitigation</p></t=
h>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p>Owner</p></th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">A</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-success">CLOSED</spa=
n></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><time datetime=3D"2024-05-14" class=3D"date-past">14 May 2024</time>&nbs=
p;</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>There is no indic=
ation of returned payment in original payment details</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">User cannot reach to=
 the returned payment from original payment details.</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">A</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-success">CLOSED</spa=
n></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><time datetime=3D"2024-05-14" class=3D"date-past">14 May 2024</time>&nbs=
p;</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>We cannot reach f=
rom the original payment to the returned payment in PODS. Hence we can't sh=
ow it the return indication in original payment details.</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">&nbsp;we can't show =
it the return indication in original payment details.</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><br></p>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">D</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-success">CLOSED</spa=
n></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><time datetime=3D"2024-05-16" class=3D"date-past">16 May 2024</time>&nbs=
p;</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>New Payment listi=
ng CAP API will have paymentId (receipt number) for all payments to be used=
 in payment details API call.</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>This properties w=
ill be used in the user journey when they need to see a payment details.</p=
></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><a href=3D"https://c=
onfluence.srv.westpac.com.au/x/FRH2X" rel=3D"nofollow">Payment listing CAP =
API</a> will return paymentId in its response,</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">D</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-success">CLOSED</spa=
n></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><time datetime=3D"2024-05-21" class=3D"date-past">21 May 2024</time>&nbs=
p;</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>We need <strong>r=
eversalIndicator </strong>property to be exposed in the payment details API=
.</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">This property is nee=
ded to show the reversal banner in the UI.</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">This is planned for =
version 2 of payment details API.</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M062091" =
href=3D"/display/~M062091" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1504078445" data-link=
ed-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-=
url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Amandeep Singh</a>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"L186784" =
href=3D"/display/~L186784" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1359031730" data-link=
ed-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-=
url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Unknown User (l186784)</a>&nb=
sp;</p>
</div></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">I</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-error">NEW</span></p=
>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><time datetime=3D"2024-09-16" class=3D"date-past">16 Sep 2024</time>&nbs=
p;</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Summary of change=
s due to <a href=3D"https://jira.srv.westpac.com.au/browse/ART-17050" class=
=3D"external-link" title=3D"https://jira.srv.westpac.com.au/browse/art-1705=
0" rel=3D"nofollow">[ART-17050]</a>:</p><p><br></p><p><strong>AS-IS:&nbsp;<=
/strong></p><p><br></p><p>When we submit a payment through W1C Portal, the =
payload field <code>creationDateTime</code> gets set by the EXP API. This f=
ield is then captured in POM and returned the to UI. This is then displayed=
 as <strong>Submitted date </strong><code>16 Sep 2024, 1:52:35pm (AEST)</co=
de></p><p><br></p><p>But, that date does actually not match the NPP PAG sub=
mission date, making payment returns impossible.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><=
/td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong>INTRODUCE=
D FOR NOV ERM24</strong><br><br>
 For transfers, or payment type where there is no NPP submission, the value=
 could be undefined. To cater for this, Payment APIs / PODS should map the =
POM creation date to this field. This enables the UI to work as IS.</p><p><=
br></p><p>For NPP Payment that are not realtime (eg held up for fraud etc),=
 we will need a temporary value to show submitted date in the UI (this is c=
urrently out of scope)</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Difference time between 'Su=
bmitted date' in Payment Review screen and Payment Detail</strong> screen: =
this change only impacts the date in the Payment Detail screen. Because of =
that, there might be a difference in value between the 2 screens . It's exp=
ected to only be of a small variance as the NPP submission happens real tim=
e.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>Summary: no direct change needed in Channels - ad=
ditional work might be required to handle non-realtime NPP payments.&nbsp;<=
/p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><strong>TO-BE:</s=
trong></p><p><br></p><p>To make payment returns work, <strong>Payment Detai=
ls INF API</strong> will map <code>creationDateTime</code> not to the value=
 of the EXP anymore, but the value of the NPP submission.</p><p><br></p><p>=
Since NPP submission is real-time, we do not expect this field to have a bi=
g variance of the <code>creationDateTime</code> set by the EXP API. Hence, =
the value we will show in the Payment Details UI will still be representati=
ve.</p><p><br></p><p>NOV ERM:&nbsp;</p><p><span>creationDateTime =3D NPP ti=
mestamp or &nbsp;EXP timestamp(for on-me and on-platform)</span></p><p><br>=
</p><p><span>FEB ERM:&nbsp;</span></p><p><span>creationDateTime =3D EXP API=
 creationDateTime/POM creationDateTime</span></p><p>NPPC<span>reationDateTi=
me =3D NPP createDatetime (new field in Payment Details API)</span></p></td=
>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M064401" =
href=3D"/display/~M064401" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1309836187" data-link=
ed-resource-version=3D"2" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-=
url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Bobby Joseph</a> <a class=3D"=
confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M062091" href=3D"/displa=
y/~M062091" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1504078445" data-linked-resource-ver=
sion=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-url=3D"https://=
confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Amandeep Singh</a> <a class=3D"confluence-us=
erlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M061387" href=3D"/display/~M061387" d=
ata-linked-resource-id=3D"1359044573" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" da=
ta-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-url=3D"https://confluence.sr=
v.westpac.com.au">Thomas Van Deun</a>&nbsp;</p>
</div></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
